author: djd
msg: DERBY-2775 Remove last use of DataTypeDescriptor.setNullability() to make DTD's use immutable wrt nullability. Fixes DERBY-3346 and DERBY-3342 which were cases when a query was getting the incorrect nullability for some columns due to the mutability of DTD when shared across nodes.
